articles.title: Martha Stewart, 81, becomes oldest Sports Illustrated swimsuit cover model - The Guardian
articles.description: Television personality says posing for the magazine’s annual swimsuit edition is ‘kind of historic’ – and that her friend Snoop Dogg will think it is ‘fantastic’
articles.content:
